Toggle overdub (ability to play and record at the same time) :
transport > transport options > overdub (on/off)

Mic not recognized :
- make sure the mic is available and on, in pulseaudio control
- turn off overdub
- unplug mic
- transport > rescan audio devices
- select : ALSA | sysdefault | 2 (stereo) | sysdefault
- plug mic in
